{"tid":213634,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"高手示範: 超陰方法 100% 假冒 www.apple.com 網址！","createTime":"2017-04-23T09:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T14:30:29.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"434e6cc0d412753a8c0d7bfd7ca3c859ed6cf8b7","tid":213634,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:17:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">大陸高手示範: 超陰方法 100% 假冒 www. apple. com 網址！<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.price.com.hk/news/2017/04/21/12/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E9%AB%98%E6%89%8B%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84-%E8%B6%85%E9%99%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95-100-%E5%81%87%E5%86%92-wwwapplecom-%E7%B6%B2%E5%9D%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fnews%2F2017%2F04%2F21%2F12%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%25AF%2584-%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%2599%25B0%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B3%2595-100-%25E5%2581%2587%25E5%2586%2592-wwwapplecom-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%259D%2580&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAndibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e1ce961a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.price.com.hk/news/2017/04/21/12/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E9%AB%98%E6%89%8B%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84-%E8%B6%85%E9%99%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95-100-%E5%81%87%E5%86%92-wwwapplecom-%E7%B6%B2%E5%9D%80</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.price.com.hk/space/news/images/20170421/88b2870fdaebf6c69bfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fspace%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F20170421%2F88b2870fdaebf6c69bfa.jpg&h=61140359&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n有上網的人都應該見過一些假冒網站，例如之前就有不少假冒 Apple ID 登入網頁來偷帳戶。不過這些假冒網站大部分都有一大弱點：網址總是奇奇怪怪，有留意就能一眼分出。不過現在竟然有方法完美假冒網址！<br />\n<br />\n大陸保安研究員發表這個完美假冒網址的方法，希望大家留意和小心，同時要引起各大瀏覽器公司的注意。方法就是利用 Unicode 格式的字來模仿正常的 ASCII 格式字。例如只要註冊這個 Unicode 網址：&ldquo;<a href=\"http://xn--pple-43d.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fxn--pple-43d.com&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAndibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=0329cf8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">xn--pple-43d.com</a>&rdquo;，在瀏覽器的網址列就會顯示為 &ldquo;<a href=\"http://аpple.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%D0%B0pple.com&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAndibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e1decdc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">аpple.com</a>&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.price.com.hk/space/news/images/20170421/acf3756301ab27185d4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fspace%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F20170421%2Facf3756301ab27185d4b.png&h=33c1b50a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n為了示範這個方法是真的，研究員特別開了一個 demo 網頁 &ndash; <a href=\"https://www.xn--80ak6aa92e.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xn--80ak6aa92e.com&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAndibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d62d00af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.xn--80ak6aa92e.com</a> 進入後只會見到 Hey there!，但再看看網址列就會見到 <a href=\"https://www.apple.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAndibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a7e3c5d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com</a>。理論上只要黑客用心製作網頁內容，要騙人這是真正的 Apple 官網就容易得多。<br />\n<br />\n這個漏洞並不能騙過 Safari (會見到真正的網址)，但 Chrome、Firefox、Opera 全都中招。好消息是今日漏洞公開後，Google 已經極速推出更新填補。以後大家就算見到網址正確，亦要留意其他東西是否有可疑。"},{"pid":"9adef62642b62bb2eb7082ecbea19fca53c48fa1","tid":213634,"uid":3363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:19:15.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"2824c6bd4927700ef5bc2607468f71adee938afc","tid":213634,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"超陰!"},{"pid":"b962242e163207a03bf93e2bc987f10acf359c51","tid":213634,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:59:35.000Z","msg":"а(俄文) 同  a(英文) 嘅分別<br />\n之前都有個<span style=\"color: red;\">раура</span>l 紅字係西爾里字母"},{"p